OL,3,CFamily of mum killed by falling tree
OL,4,Cbranch set up foundation in her memory
OL,6,FThe husband of a mum-of-two who was
OL,7,Fkilled by a falling tree branch has
OL,8,Fset up a foundation in her memory to
OL,9,Fhelp local children.
OL,11,FMadia Kauser, 32, was walking with her
OL,12,Fhusband and children in Witton Park in
OL,13,FBlackburn on 11 August 2025, when she
OL,14,Fwas struck by a branch.
OL,16,FHer husband Wasim Khan has set up a
OL,17,Ffoundation in her name to raise money
OL,18,Ffor 'children in Blackburn who suffer
OL,19,Ffrom poverty'.
