OL,6,FMr Khan said Madia "would honestly
OL,7,Fgive her last ten pounds in her pocket
OL,8,Fif she seen a child struggle".
OL,10,FHe said: "That's what kind of heart
OL,11,Fshe had. So why can't we all do the
OL,12,Fsame?
OL,14,F"Real help starts in our own local
OL,15,Fcommunity."
OL,17,FA charity walk to kick-start the
OL,18,Ffundraising efforts has been planned
OL,19,Ffor 7 February. The route will start
OL,20,Fat Blackburn's Pleasington Cemetery
OL,21,Fand then up Pendle Hill.
