OL,6,FMr Khan said: "We will be walking up
OL,7,FPendle Hill on February 7 and anyone
OL,8,Fis welcome.
OL,10,F"The reason for this walk is in her
OL,11,Fmemory. I want people to understand
OL,12,Fshe was so unselfish.
OL,14,F"The main reason why is I want to try
OL,15,Fraise money to help kids similar ages
OL,16,Fto mine who are struggling with hunger
OL,17,For poverty.
OL,19,F"I want to donate all the funds to
OL,20,Flocal families struggling directly in
OL,21,FBlackburn on behalf of her."
