OL,9,FAn inquest into Madia Kauser's death
OL,10,Fwas opened in August.
OL,12,FIn November 2025, Blackburn with
OL,13,FDarwen Council was served with an
OL,14,Fimprovement notice by the Health and
OL,15,FSafety Executive, and last month
OL,16,Fapproved a new policy on the
OL,17,Fmanagement of the borough's trees.
